      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experiments used bovine blood at 37°C with hematocrit 35±2%. VAD COU specifies human blood at 37°C with hematocrit 40%. Viscosity correction applied but species difference in red blood cell fragility is not accounted for. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
