      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on literature precedent for rotating blood pump flows. Power Law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) used without comparison to alternative formulations (Arora, Taskin). Sensitivity of NIH to hemolysis model exponent is characterized via Monte Carlo but alternative model forms are not evaluated. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
